{"tid":1193001,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日就出發 小小感言","createTime":"2019-06-08T17:01:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T17:07:53.000Z","uid":84396,"like":24,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a800019067ae509c79824b917d4f04f87332f7ca","tid":1193001,"uid":84396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T17:01:05.000Z","msg":"唔知係咪開錯台 如果錯左既講定聲Sorry<br />\n<br />\n當年928 自己一個 滿腔熱血就上左街 唔敢話自己衝得最前 但親眼見過舉旗 催淚彈 胡椒噴霧 訓過街頭 避過追捕<br />\n當年仲係學生哥<br />\n<br />\n事隔五年 終於又一次掀起反抗運動 但呢次好可能真係最後一次 聽日發生咩事其實大家都唔知 其實我都好驚會變得比928更加激烈<br />\n<br />\n但係... 驚一日定驚一世？我寧願搏一鋪<br />\n<br />\n香港人其實真係好自私 自私到為自己未來爭取自由同保障都可能變成罪行 但如果大家仲想呼吸到自由既空氣<br />\n聽日出一出黎 多你一個就係多一個<br />\n<br />\n唔敢講太多 大家做好準備 早啲休息<br />\n聽日6.9 我地街上見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不散 香港 香港人加油<br />\n<br />\nSorry for 1999"},{"pid":"7aec0ac47656ca73ec71ad5afb9a138f98e99c79","tid":1193001,"uid":130406,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T17:03:04.000Z","msg":"[雨傘的教訓] 必須反守為攻 一鼓作氣 佔路無用<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1189418\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1189418</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"12b31a5fe09d1bc4ebb0fbd2d88d2f0c99e10ce7","tid":1193001,"uid":52230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T17:03:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>槍口一致對外！<br />\n<br />\n不要分化！不要懷疑隊友！<br />\n<br />\n有人被捕立即群擁而上集體救援！<br />\n<br />\n勿比機會警犬單獨拉走同伴！<br />\n<br />\n一切行動必須群體出發！ <br />\n<br />\nStick Together Team! 不要落單！<br />\n<br />\n6.9 GOGOGO!</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>唔衝嘅人幫手拖住篤灰狗 <br />\n<br />\n衝嘅巴繼續上前！<br />\n<br />\n齊心！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"351613a65661fbb3593e56c0851269a2e88c50b6","tid":1193001,"uid":55493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T17:04:16.000Z","msg":"志氣"},{"pid":"dafd65744796d0d8a61c980e3fb5c190b5b15038","tid":1193001,"uid":195350,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T17:05:27.000Z","msg":"同你感覺一樣"},{"pid":"7a2ce3350b0d0b7b86ecfea386693749da0baca4","tid":1193001,"uid":84396,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T17:05:44.000Z","msg":"各位唔好灰心 呢一刻未係時候灰心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d059b067a489d3bcbb078eff1adbd01207cc01f2","tid":1193001,"uid":59081,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T17:07:53.000Z","msg":"當日仲返緊大學雨革時全班都出哂去<br />\n今日出左黎做野但點都會出黎<br />\n成功與否冇人知 出左黎再算"}]}